metadata.name: Happy time
metadata.description:
AUTOLOVE project

HAPPY TIME

One day after the shooting, I decided to lie down to rest, exhausted, and in a lucid dream, images of an audiovisual album came to me, which I named AUTOLOVE. 
The presented photos show the work of the last couple of years on the site of absurdity and kitsch, religion and sinfulness and love.

35mm film
